 HOW TO BUY DOGE CEO - DOWNLOAD & SETUP METAMASK OR TRUSTWALLET

Download MetaMask (a crypto wallet in the form of a browser extension) and
TrustWallet (an app for your phone). After that you will have to add the
Binance Smart Chain to your network-list.

BUY AND SEND BNB TO METAMASK

Buy BNB on an exchange (i.e. Binance, Kraken, Coinbase etc.). Transfer the
tokens to your MetaMask wallet address. BEP-20 addresses start with a "0x".

HEAD ON TO PANCAKESWAP

Head on over to PancakeSwap and use the Contract Address to find the Token.
Set the slippage tolerance to 12% (but could be higher depending on how much
demand there is).

VIEW AND HODL

Swap BNB for the Token. Now you need to add it to your MetaMask or Trust
Wallet to view your current holdings. Lastly, HODL!

Hello Doge CEO community! 🐕‍🦺

Just a fellow crypto enthusiast passing by, but couldn't help noticing your impressive project. The $DOGECEO token is truly taking the meme game to another level. 

We all love a good meme, but you know what's even better? Having tools to grow your community and increase the utility of your token. Imagine having your own DEX or Lottery, where the house always wins (and by house, we mean the community!). Or maybe a multicurrency wallet to store your beloved $DOGECEO tokens and other cryptos. 

We offer a range of B2B tools - from DEX and Lottery to Wallet, Farming, DAO, CrossChain, and IDOFactory. And the best part? Most of them are revenue share tools, meaning you don't have to pay unless you're earning. 

For example, our DEX tool allows you to create your own DEX based on Uniswap V2, with commission rates from 0.00% to 20%. Or our Lottery tool, a blockchain-based lottery where you can earn 0-30% commission. 

And let's not forget about our Wallet tool. For just $999, you can create a multicurrency crypto wallet with features like P2P exchange via atomic swaps, customize tokens, set commissions, and Visa/MC integration. 

We're not here to play, we're here to help you create. Interested? Check out our demo at https://t.me/onoutdemos. And remember, in the world of crypto, the only limit is your imagination. 🚀

PS: If Doge CEO ever needs a CFO, I'm available. I accept payment in $DOGECEO tokens. 😉
